{"tid":2435362,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"日本興奮討論《日本可愛女主播很會摸龜頭》越摸越粗越摸越長...","createTime":"2021-03-06T07:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T03:37:53.000Z","uid":147522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"074b9f9a8fc9640996d914c6406f3571283ab642","tid":2435362,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"日本電視節目探訪世界的珍獸，只見畫面上日本可愛女主播很會摸龜頭 ，動作嫻熟熟練，龜頭被摸得很舒服也就越伸越長，脖子越摸越粗......讓網友們看得好興奮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好大大的珍獸「陸龜」<br />\n共有11層40種（或42種），除了大洋洲和南極洲以外，世界各地均有分佈。龜，也是四大靈獸「龍、鳳凰、麒麟、龜」當中唯一真實存在的祥瑞珍獸。傳說龜會飲吸天地山川的靈氣，所以特別長壽，被視為能延壽的祥瑞象徵。<br />\n<br />\n日本節目探訪世界珍獸，請女主持人摸摸陸龜的頭，大概是被摸得很舒服，龜龜忍不住把頭伸長連脖子也變粗還越來越挺，然後就被興奮的網友做成GIF檔了。下流！<br />\n<br />\n1991年出生的這個正妹主持人叫做「森遙香」，是位女主播。出身自日本宮城縣，從高校時代就參與放送部的她，還曾擔任第90屆全國高校棒球選手權大賽的開幕司儀，後來在筑波大學專研人文、言語學畢業，獲獎無數後進入KHB東日本放送，是才貌雙全的正妹主播啊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJ5Lh88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJ5Lh88.png&h=ef0a81ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rh7qh9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRh7qh9c.png&h=fb6d7d28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAjPKPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAjPKPg.png&h=ca863e8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b542ae6da1c1cb724b04ec0b47f7c738c95b03f","tid":2435362,"uid":313222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff618dd1e60a19713aba931d6ec76140724a115","tid":2435362,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b542ae6da1c1cb724b04ec0b47f7c738c95b03f","tid":2435362,"uid":313222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf0295ebec345bdba947762afae67a52233849b","tid":2435362,"uid":321843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"出返去先"},{"pid":"8404e8da4ab72c2dbea29b261a49b0cdfb80da1d","tid":2435362,"uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"冇gif 0/10"},{"pid":"7c969ab121051dc486c0fe8b2c1cc119cc6e2a14","tid":2435362,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"冇gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}